{"type": "article", "id": 2907, "title": "折叠型海绵洗碗布", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-17T08:04:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232344JEci20rSHbTd3hBv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t海绵清洁布算是很常见的厨房清洁用品了吧，日前，韩国设计师 Yoon Naera 却对这一不起眼的小物件进行了重新设计，将黄色海绵部分挖掉了一块，用绿色的硬质丝网部分填充，这样就形成了一个折叠型的洗碗布，轻轻松松就可以把玻璃杯壁、碗口、盘子等其他餐具放在中间挖空的部分，只是一个简单的改造，就让擦洗工作变得更加方便快捷。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232343JTWrbgzADuV0s94y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.45625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232343XFMYZIfx7t9yjuNm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6484375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232344Q6hZgxCpBRnF8Tbo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}